mil.nga.giat.geowave.ingest

Interface DataAdapterProvider<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - the java type for the data being ingested
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IngestPluginBase<I,O>, IngestWithMapper<I,O>, IngestWithReducer<I,K,V,O>, LocalFileIngestPlugin<O>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLocalIngestWithMapper, GeoLifeIngestPlugin, GeoLifeIngestPlugin.IngestGeoLifeFromHdfs, GeoToolsRasterDataStoreIngestPlugin, GeoToolsVectorDataStoreIngestPlugin, GpxIngestPlugin, GpxIngestPlugin.IngestGpxTrackFromHdfs, TdriveIngestPlugin, TdriveIngestPlugin.IngestGpxTrackFromHdfs

    public interface DataAdapterProvider<T>
    This interface is applicable for plugins that need to provide writable data adapters for ingest.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      WritableDataAdapter<T>[] getDataAdapters(String globalVisibility)
      Get all writable adapters used by this plugin

    • Method Detail

      • getDataAdapters

        WritableDataAdapter<T>[] getDataAdapters(String globalVisibility)
        Get all writable adapters used by this plugin
        Parameters:
        globalVisibility - If on the command-line the user specifies a global visibility to write to the visibility column in GeoWave, it is passed along here. It is assumed that this is the same visibility string that will be passed to IngestPluginBase.toGeoWaveData()
        Returns:
        An array of adapters that may be used by this plugin
